Package: repo.data
Title: R Repository Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Lluís", "Revilla Sancho", , "lluis.revilla@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9747-2570"))
Description: Retrieve metadata about packages from repositories in order
    to explore package dependencies, links between help pages, aliases,
    package availability on a given date, and other repository dependent
    outcome. The package provides functions that allow package
    maintainers and users to navigate changes on dependencies.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/llrs/repo.data,
        https://llrs.github.io/repo.data/
BugReports: https://github.com/llrs/repo.data/issues
